prompts.content:
Act as a professional article writer and create a comprehensive article about {{topic}} that includes:

1. Engaging headline
2. Strong introduction
3. Well-researched main points
4. Expert quotes and statistics
5. Real-world examples
6. Actionable conclusions

Target audience: {{audience}}
Tone: {{tone}}
Word count: {{wordCount}}
Style: {{style}}

Act as a technical content writer and create detailed documentation for {{subject}} that includes:

1. Technical overview
2. Step-by-step instructions
3. Code examples or technical specifications
4. Best practices
5. Troubleshooting guide
6. Reference materials

Expertise level: {{level}}
Format: {{format}}
Include diagrams: {{diagrams}}
Technical depth: {{depth}}

Act as a white paper writer and create an authoritative document about {{topic}} that includes:

1. Executive summary
2. Problem statement
3. Background research
4. Proposed solution
5. Implementation details
6. Case studies
7. ROI analysis
8. Recommendations

Industry: {{industry}}
Target readers: {{audience}}
Length: {{length}}
Focus: {{focus}}
